# Hushpot — environment template. Copy to .env (gitignored) OR use `npx hardhat vars set <NAME>`.
#
# Hardhat reads secrets via `vars.get(...)` in hardhat.config.ts. The recommended path is the
# encrypted vars store (`npx hardhat vars set MNEMONIC`), but a plain .env also works for the
# deploy script's optional overrides below.

# --- Required to deploy/test on Sepolia (set via `npx hardhat vars set ...`) ---
# MNEMONIC: 12-word seed for the deployer + member accounts (account 0 is the deployer).
#   npx hardhat vars set MNEMONIC
# INFURA_API_KEY: Sepolia RPC project key from https://infura.io
#   npx hardhat vars set INFURA_API_KEY
# ETHERSCAN_API_KEY: for `npm run verify:sepolia` (optional)
#   npx hardhat vars set ETHERSCAN_API_KEY

# --- Optional deploy override (read from process.env by deploy/00_deploy_hushpot.ts) ---
# Override the cUSDT wrapper if Zama rotates it. Defaults to the documented Sepolia address.
# CUSDT_ADDRESS=0x4E7B06D78965594eB5EF5414c357ca21E1554491
